title: Quicktax 2007 Business with Keygen
description:
Is QuickTax Platinum right for me?
If you want to get more out of your investments - from stocks & mutual funds to rental properties - QuickTax Platinum can help.

With comprehensive tools to help simplify complex tax returns, QuickTax Platinum makes it easy to minimize your taxes and optimize your deductions - even if you&#039;re using it for the first time.

Handles life changes
Changes in your personal situation impacts your taxes. QuickTax Platinum helps you understand & manage the effect of such changes - from getting married to having a baby.

Includes guidance & support
QuickTax Platinum walks you through your tax return step-by-step - which means less effort for you. Answer interview-style questions in plain English, and let QuickTax do the rest.

It even double-checks your return for errors and alerts you to money-saving opportunities.

Provides guidance for investments & retirement planning
RRSPs. Stocks & bonds. Mutual funds. Employee stock plans. You&#039;re investing now to help secure your financial future - and, as you may know, those investments can help you at tax time.

QuickTax Platinum features tools designed to help you maximize your investments so you can benefit today and at retirement.

Maximizes your deductions
QuickTax Platinum can help you optimize all your deductions - from family & spousal tax credits to prescription medications.

NEW! Uncovers hidden dollars with the Deduction Toolbox
Why worry about overlooking a deduction? QuickTax Platinum now includes the Deduction Toolbox, a series of features that appear throughout the QuickTax filing process to show you deductions you didn&#039;t even know you qualified for.

Guarantees your taxes are done right
Trusted by millions of Canadians each year, QuickTax is Canada&#039;s #1 best-selling tax software1. It&#039;s guaranteed 100% accurate2 - plus, it comes with a 60-day money back guarantee6

File online - and get $10 cash back4
Make the ECO-Choice! Prepare your return using QuickTax and file with NETFILE3 - and waste less paper by filing online. Plus, when you file with NETFILE:

* Get your refund in as little as 8 days
* QuickTax will give you $10 cash back

Helps you spend less time on your taxes
QuickTax Platinum includes time-saving features - like online filing - to make it easier for you to meet the deadline to file without compromising the quality of your return.
